trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento de <see cref="E:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection.StrokesChanged" /> .

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection.StrokesChanged> event occurs whenever a <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> is added or removed from a <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection.StrokesChanged> evento ocorre sempre que um <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> é adicionado ou removido de um <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection>.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> that contains the added strokes.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> que contém os traços adicionados.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> that contains the removed strokes.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> que contém os traços removidos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollectionChangedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollectionChangedEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the strokes that have been added to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os traços que foram adicionados ao <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> that contains the added strokes.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> que contém os traços adicionados.

trans-unit.source: Gets the strokes that have been removed from the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os traços que foram removidos do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> that contains the removed strokes.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> que contém os traços removidos.
